---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — BrainKit"
  description="Terms of Service for BrainKit, the AI productivity setup service."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen px-4 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-amber-400 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Service Description</h2>
          <p>
            BrainKit ("we", "us", "our") provides an AI productivity setup service for solo consultants
            and freelancers. The service consists of a custom configuration file (CLAUDE.md) and
            supporting materials tailored to your work context, delivered by Johannes via a remote setup
            session and follow-up email.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            By purchasing a BrainKit package you ("the client") agree to these Terms of Service in full.
            If you do not agree, do not proceed with purchase.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Payment and Refund Policy</h2>
          <p>
            All prices are quoted in USD and are payable in full at the time of purchase via Stripe.
            Applicable taxes may be added at checkout depending on your location.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Because BrainKit delivers a bespoke digital service, <strong class="text-zinc-200">no refunds
            are offered once delivery has commenced</strong>. Delivery is considered to have commenced
            when you receive the intake confirmation email following your purchase.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you have a concern before delivery begins, contact
            <a href="mailto:johannes@brainkit.so" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 transition">
              johannes@brainkit.so
            </a>
            and we will work to resolve it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Delivery</h2>
          <p>
            We aim to deliver your CLAUDE.md and supporting materials within the timeframe stated on the
            pricing page at the time of purchase. Timelines are estimates and may be affected by intake
            form completion time, scheduling availability, or circumstances outside our control.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You are responsible for completing the intake form accurately and in a timely manner.
            Significant delay on your part may push back your delivery date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            Upon delivery and receipt of full payment, you own the CLAUDE.md file and any
            personalised configuration materials we produce specifically for you. You may use, modify,
            and distribute them freely.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We retain ownership of the underlying template methodology, system design patterns, and
            any generic tooling used to produce your deliverables. Nothing in these Terms transfers
            ownership of that methodology to you.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The BrainKit starter template published on GitHub is licensed separately under the MIT
            licence; see the repository for details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to use BrainKit services or deliverables to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-2 ml-2">
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Infringe the intellectual property rights of any third party</li>
            <li>Generate, distribute, or store content that is harmful, abusive, or discriminatory</li>
            <li>Resell or sublicense the deliverables as a competing AI setup service without our prior
              written consent</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The service is provided "as is". We make no warranty that the CLAUDE.md or related
            materials will produce any specific outcome in your AI tooling, that they will be free from
            errors, or that they will remain compatible with third-party tools (such as Claude, Cursor,
            or any other AI assistant) as those tools evolve.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, BrainKit and Johannes shall not be
            liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising
            out of or related to your use of the service or deliverables, even if advised of the
            possibility of such damages.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Our total liability for any claim arising under these Terms shall not exceed the amount
            you paid for the relevant service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of
            [Governing Law Jurisdiction], without regard to its conflict of law provisions.
            Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of
            [Governing Law Jurisdiction].
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via
            email to clients with active or recent engagements. Continued use of the service after
            changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-zinc-100 text-xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about these Terms? Email
            <a href="mailto:johannes@brainkit.so" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 transition">
              johannes@brainkit.so
            </a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-800">
        <a href="/" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 transition text-sm">&larr; Back to BrainKit</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
